Description

As of March 30 2023, this project has not been issued any building permits from the Heber City Building Department. An architect has been selected. Information on a general contractor and method of selection has not been released. A firm construction timeline has not been established. *Project information, including timeline and contacts, has been obtained through public sources. The content management team continues to pursue additional details; however, the contact(s) listed have yet to disclose or confirm any information. Inquiries should be directed to the contact(s) listed.
